{"text_id":190452,"tokens":["The"," authors"," present"," an"," interesting"," approach"," to"," model","-","based"," machine"," translation",","," which"," is"," based"," on"," deco","ders"," that"," are"," trained"," with"," different"," objective"," functions"," and"," then"," combined"," into"," one"," single"," decoder"," using"," linear"," combination"," weights"," learned"," from"," data",".","\n","This"," work"," has"," several"," advantages"," over"," previous"," approaches"," in"," this"," area"," (","e",".","g",".,"," Moses","):"," it"," allows"," us"," to"," combine"," models"," without"," having"," access"," to"," their"," internal"," parameters",";"," it"," can"," be"," applied"," to"," any"," type"," of"," statistical"," MT"," systems",";"," and"," it"," does"," not"," require"," tuning"," additional"," hyper","parameters"," such"," as"," beam"," size"," or"," number"," of"," features"," used"," by"," each"," individual"," component"," model","."," The"," experiments"," show"," promising"," results"," when"," combining"," two"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," SMT"," systems"," built"," upon"," very"," different"," architectures"," -"," namely"," phrase","-","based"," decoding"," vs"," neural"," network"," language"," modeling","."," ","\n","However",","," I"," have"," some"," concerns"," about"," how"," well"," these"," methods"," generalize"," beyond"," the"," specific"," datasets"," they"," were"," tested"," on",":"],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"bloomz","label":1}